### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@sessionId = test-session-123
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Get cart
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart?sessionId={{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Add item to cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "productId": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Remove item from cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "itemId": "CART_ITEM_ID_HERE"
}

### Clear cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart?sessionId={{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Transfer cart to user (after login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}"
}